{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Korean BBQ Simulator</h2>Test your grilling skills in this fun and wacky - *cough* I mean, totally realistic physics-based meat grilling game based on Korean cuisine. This passion-project is a revival and re-envisioning of the classic Yakiniku and Meat Grilling games that were popular in Korea and Japan.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Different Modes for the Brave</h2>Challenge yourself with three different difficulties, three different modes, and a plethora of meats to cook.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137620/extras/menu.PNG?t=1689783422\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Take Control and Turn Up the Heat</h2>Meats cook at different rates, be sure to adjust the grill's heat to match the type of meat you are cooking! <br>Eating raw or burnt meat can result in a penalty to your score and a stomach ache! Learn to master cooking multiple meats at the same time for maximum points!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137620/extras/Hanu_Grilling.PNG?t=1689783422\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Become the Ultimate Korean BBQ Master</h2>Compete in online leaderboards against your friends, or even strangers around the world.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137620/extras/Score.PNG?t=1689783422\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Time Grilling","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2137620/19d3951f3ec4b4f4b3037f758c2d9fdb48fd17aa.jpg"},{"name":"Messy Eater","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2137620/aafd1ff37483588caf611f59cddbd52e82e2b94d.jpg"},{"name":"Kimchi Lover","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2137620/ca937b088dfaf4624bffe1197ac66d3c388ae547.jpg"},{"name":"Who You Going to Call?","path":"https://cdn.aka